---
title: Stuffed Squash Boats with Mushrooms, Quinoa, and Golden Raisins
description: Why dirty an extra bowl when you can use the squash itself? That’s what our chefs, Freida and Nate, were thinking when they started experimenting with delicata squash. Golden raisins and tangy feta make an appearance here to add a touch of sweetness and creaminess to the dish.
